Class MessageWriterDelegateImplBase

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.mts.base.MessageWriterDelegateImplBase
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageWriter
public class MessageWriterDelegateImplBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageWriter

Convenience class for aspects which define MessageWriter delegate classes. It implements all methods by delegating to another instance, given in the constructor. Aspect inner classes which extend this need only implement specific methods that are relevant to that aspect,
